parts.text:
```json
{
"application": "PBS",
"details": {
"software": {
"felixsim": "executable for simulating electron diffraction patterns",
"felixdraw": "executable for generating 2D images from diffraction patterns",
"txt2png.py": "Python script for converting text data to PNG images"
},
"resources": {
"cores": "number of CPU cores to use (default: 1)",
"wtime": "maximum wall clock time for the job (default: 00:10:00)",
"ranks": "number of MPI ranks to use (default: cores)",
"nodes": "number of nodes to use (default: cores)",
"mppwidth": "number of MPI tasks per node (default: 4)",
"ompthreads": "number of OpenMP threads per MPI task (default: 1)",
"pvmem": "memory per node (default: 400mb)",
"budget_account": "account to charge the job to (optional)"
},
"environment_variables": {
"PBS_O_WORKDIR": "absolute path to the working directory",
"basedir": "directory where the job was submitted",
"binarydir": "directory containing the FelixSIM and FelixDRAW executables",
"tmpdir": "temporary directory for running the job",
"MPICH_RANK_REORDER_METHOD": "set to 1 for optimal MPI performance",
"MPICH_PTL_MATCH_OFF": "set to 1 for optimal MPI performance",
"MPICH_FAST_MEMCPY": "set to 1 for optimal MPI performance",
"IPATH_NO_CPUAFFINITY": "set to 1 to disable CPU affinity settings",
"OMP_NUM_THREADS": "number of OpenMP threads to use"
},
"input_files": {
"felix.cif": "crystallographic information file (CIF)",
"felix.sca": "scattering factor file"
},
"output_files": {
"inpfile": "input file for FelixSIM",
"targetdir": "directory for storing simulation results"
},
"script_structure": {
"loops": {
"ncif": "loop over three CIF files in different directories",
"writeind": "loop over writing flags (0-10)",
"imageind1": "loop over image flags (0-2)",
"imageind2": "loop over image flags (0-2)",
"imageind3": "loop over image flags (0-2)",
"binorind": "loop over binarization flags (0-1)",
"scatterind": "loop over scattering factor flags (0-2)",
"centralind": "loop over central beam flags (0-1)",
"maskind": "loop over masking flags (0-1)",
"zolzind": "loop over ZOLZ flags (0-1)",
"absorbind": "loop over absorption flags (0-1)",
"anisodebyeind": "loop over anisotropic Debye-Waller factor flags (0-1)",
"xdirind": "loop over X-direction flags (0-1)"
},
"commands": {
"mkdir": "create directory",
"cp": "copy files",
"rm": "remove files or directories",
"touch": "create empty file",
"echo": "print text to the terminal",
"cat": "concatenate files",
"ls": "list directory contents",
"mpirun": "run an MPI executable",
"wait": "wait for background processes to finish",
"chmod": "change file permissions",
"qsub": "submit a job to the PBS queue"
}
}
}
```
